Ansiblee Introduction 

Most popular open-source automation tool 
No special software on remote host 

Linux learning? 

it uses the same methods as an administration  like SSH, WinRM, API 

simple to work with 
- uses YAML automation scripts called playbooks 
- you don't have to be a programmer!!!
- it's human readable with just a logic flow 


cross platform compatible 
- if its a piece of IT infrastructure you need to manage, ansible can automate it!!!

active community 
- find and use exxisiting automation

to connect to automation (ansible architecture) 
local execution 
- connecting to routers or switches, things like APIs 
- ansible controller, servier runs ansible 
- API commands are sent directly 

and remote execution 
- the execution is sent from the remote host 
